OL,5,G1000 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FAt the Who'd a Thought It in Kent,
OL,7,     FJoe and Alex start the week in
OL,8,     Fstyle with complimentary
OL,9,     Fchampagne. But guest Brian's not
OL,10,     Fso bubbly at breakfast, after the
OL,11,     Fnoisy hot tub kept him awake.
OL,12,G1035 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FOwner Matthew and entertainment
OL,14,     Fmanager Liam welcome their rivals
OL,15,     Fto their family-friendly B&B, the
OL,16,     FNew Osborne Hotel, in Blackpool.
OL,17,     FBut there are grumbles about room
OL,18,     Fsize and cleanliness.
